45:31.361 --> 45:35.181
♪ Sing His mercy and His grace ♪

45:35.231 --> 45:37.551
♪ In the mansion ♪

45:37.601 --> 45:39.481
♪ Bright and blessed ♪

45:39.531 --> 45:43.321
♪ He'll prepare for us a place ♪

45:43.371 --> 45:45.361
♪ When we all ♪

45:45.411 --> 45:47.861
♪ Get to Heaven ♪

45:47.911 --> 45:50.331
♪ What a day of rejoicing that will be ♪

45:50.381 --> 45:51.601
[both moaning]

