46:09.761 --> 46:13.521
TOBY: It's been three days.
The press is starting to sniff.

46:13.571 --> 46:17.361
Fine, we'll make a "no
stone unturned" statement.

46:17.411 --> 46:19.891
We have any bones we can throw out there?

46:19.941 --> 46:21.461
The last time anybody saw Shane,

46:21.511 --> 46:24.091
he was picking up his
uniform from a dry cleaners.

46:24.141 --> 46:25.561
[device beeps]

46:25.611 --> 46:28.001
We have surveillance
footage of the parking lot.

46:29.951 --> 46:32.571
We got footage of a truck that's there

46:32.621 --> 46:34.741
at the same time, same place.

46:34.791 --> 46:38.411
It belongs to our suspect, Keith Dennison.

46:38.531 --> 46:41.681
He's got a very violent history.

46:41.731 --> 46:43.581
We pulled Shane's phone records

46:43.631 --> 46:45.151
and got multiple pings off a tower

46:45.201 --> 46:49.091
near the halfway house
where Dennison lives.

46:49.241 --> 46:53.831
- You arrest the guy?
- Not enough PC yet.

46:53.881 --> 46:57.161
But you know what's funny?

46:57.211 --> 46:59.901
He was locked up on an assault with
a deadly weapons charge last week.

46:59.951 --> 47:01.871
Well, what the fuck? Why was he out?

47:01.921 --> 47:04.771
The judge let him go.

47:06.621 --> 47:08.311
Want to guess who the judge was?

48:24.971 --> 48:28.091
[dog barking in distance]

48:39.851 --> 48:41.431
[knife clicks]

48:44.761 --> 48:46.311
[grunts]

48:47.761 --> 48:49.441
[sighs]

48:57.131 --> 48:58.891
Hey, bud.

48:58.941 --> 49:02.121
Looky what I got.

49:02.171 --> 49:04.521
What are you gonna put it in?

49:04.571 --> 49:10.101
Um... I'll think of something.

49:12.921 --> 49:15.201
CRYSTAL: You know, you never asked me.

49:15.251 --> 49:18.811
Well, for God sakes,
Crystal, it's just a fish.

49:18.861 --> 49:21.541
No, I'm talking about PJ,

49:21.591 --> 49:24.241
