49:24.291 --> 49:26.211
[monitor beeping]

49:26.261 --> 49:28.981
Did I need to?

49:29.031 --> 49:31.421
I don't think we see it the same.

49:33.301 --> 49:35.961
I think PJ's gone, and
I'd like to bury our son.

49:36.011 --> 49:38.531
Well, you're wrong, Crystal.

49:38.581 --> 49:41.801
Now, you got to trust me on this.

49:41.851 --> 49:43.761
God kept PJ alive for a reason.

49:43.811 --> 49:46.001
